WEBVTT

01:51.810 --> 01:57.300
[The Legend of Rosy Clouds]

01:58.539 --> 02:01.870
[Episode 27]

02:23.800 --> 02:26.710
-Beat him! He deserves to die!
-Shameless!

02:26.710 --> 02:29.520
-Exactly!
-Screw him!

02:29.920 --> 02:31.600
You shameless wretch!

02:31.930 --> 02:33.920
-He deserves to die! Hit him!
-Shame on you!

02:33.920 --> 02:37.270
-That's him!
-Shameless wretch!

02:44.630 --> 02:45.630
Zheng Yi,

02:47.400 --> 02:49.079
tell me—

02:49.730 --> 02:53.130
do I have to accept getting old?

02:54.960 --> 02:55.910
Master,

02:55.930 --> 02:57.730
you should never think that way.

02:57.930 --> 02:59.079
If you do,

02:59.150 --> 03:01.150
it will play right into their hands.

03:02.400 --> 03:04.560
I, Zheng Yuan,

03:05.680 --> 03:09.080
have served as an official
at the imperial court for decades,

03:10.050 --> 03:12.010
yet it was the first time

03:13.010 --> 03:14.080
I had ever

03:15.050 --> 03:16.860
experienced that.

03:18.400 --> 03:19.020
Master,

03:19.400 --> 03:21.200
they just don't understand you!

03:21.320 --> 03:22.450
But there will always be

03:22.450 --> 03:24.180
someone who does in this world!

03:26.210 --> 03:27.470
Don't take it to heart.

03:29.079 --> 03:30.079
Master Zheng Tao

03:30.640 --> 03:32.610
wrote to you a while ago, didn't he?

03:33.490 --> 03:34.380
I think

03:35.329 --> 03:37.329
maybe we should return to Jing City,

03:37.680 --> 03:39.140
so you can rest for a while.

03:54.000 --> 03:55.120
You may get up.

04:21.760 --> 04:22.560
Grandfather,

04:22.850 --> 04:24.180
what happened outside?

04:24.210 --> 04:25.740
What's all that fuss about?

04:31.490 --> 04:32.280
Is Fan Yun

04:33.880 --> 04:34.800
doing alright?

04:40.409 --> 04:42.090
Nine Cities is in danger.

04:43.320 --> 04:44.780
The nobles are in trouble.

04:45.050 --> 04:47.050
Our Zheng family is facing a crisis.

04:48.050 --> 04:49.850
It has come to this point,

04:51.050 --> 04:53.310
and you're still thinking about Fan Yun?

04:54.090 --> 04:56.290
Grandfather, you care about the world,

04:56.560 --> 04:58.290
but what have you gotten in return?

04:58.290 --> 04:59.490
Nothing but the Governor's resentment

04:59.490 --> 05:00.890
and the people's hatred.

05:03.050 --> 05:03.850
Shi...

05:06.650 --> 05:09.120
In a place as big as Nine Cities,

05:09.120 --> 05:11.310
sometimes you need

05:11.730 --> 05:14.420
a so-called villain.

05:16.000 --> 05:19.680
Tough and drastic measures are

05:20.120 --> 05:23.850
necessary to ensure its survival.

05:26.800 --> 05:28.410
Ordinary people can

05:29.680 --> 05:32.409
easily let their emotions
get the better of them.

05:32.530 --> 05:33.730
Sometimes,

05:33.730 --> 05:37.190
they need to be ruled with an iron fist.

05:38.970 --> 05:40.930
I'm sacrificing myself

05:41.680 --> 05:45.760
for the greater good of Nine Cities!

05:46.730 --> 05:48.440
Everyone wants to be a saint,

05:49.090 --> 05:51.290
be a good guy,

05:52.090 --> 05:54.409
and make everyone happy.

05:58.200 --> 05:59.120
If we do that...

06:00.760 --> 06:01.850
If we do that,

06:04.800 --> 06:06.000
it'll lead to nothing

06:06.120 --> 06:08.440
but terrible disaster.

06:11.240 --> 06:12.900
Please forgive my bluntness.

06:15.090 --> 06:16.000
Go ahead.

06:17.530 --> 06:18.650
You are wrong, Grandfather.

06:18.650 --> 06:20.380
Because it's just not worth it.

06:20.530 --> 06:22.320
You brat!

06:28.100 --> 06:30.100
Who says it's not worth it?

06:37.300 --> 06:38.500
Shi...

06:40.810 --> 06:42.540
From today on,

06:44.420 --> 06:46.860
I can't keep you here anymore.

06:46.890 --> 06:48.570
You're beyond my control.

06:54.010 --> 06:55.680
You literally are...

08:21.650 --> 08:22.650
Young Master Shi,

08:23.090 --> 08:24.290
are you alright?

08:25.290 --> 08:25.880
Uncle Yi.

08:31.360 --> 08:32.270
Where is my grandfather?

08:32.270 --> 08:34.870
Master asked me
to escort you back to your room.

08:38.770 --> 08:40.130
Is he still mad at me?

08:40.600 --> 08:42.010
Master

08:42.130 --> 08:45.080
just couldn't swallow his pride
to come over.

08:47.680 --> 08:48.530
I knew that

08:48.950 --> 08:51.610
Grandfather wouldn't
truly hold it against me.

09:01.990 --> 09:03.610
I'm well aware of the purpose

09:03.730 --> 09:04.980
of your visit.

09:05.940 --> 09:07.400
And I also understand

09:08.080 --> 09:09.810
all your painstaking efforts.

09:11.370 --> 09:12.370
Come on.

09:12.960 --> 09:14.420
Let's have another drink.

09:15.250 --> 09:15.960
Cheers.

09:15.960 --> 09:16.700
Zheng.

09:19.600 --> 09:20.930
I'll only drink this

09:21.650 --> 09:23.850
if you admit that you are really getting

09:24.560 --> 09:26.090
senile and muddle-headed.

09:26.770 --> 09:27.930
I admit it.

09:29.170 --> 09:29.630
Cheers.

09:31.370 --> 09:32.530
Only if you two

09:32.530 --> 09:33.800
stop being so stubborn

09:33.800 --> 09:35.010
will I drink this.

09:37.440 --> 09:38.250
I promise you.

09:39.840 --> 09:40.810
Zheng,

09:41.410 --> 09:43.210
after the epidemic in Yong City,

09:43.600 --> 09:46.650
I actually have growing confidence

09:46.650 --> 09:48.680
in the young Governor and Fan Yun.

09:50.250 --> 09:51.800
And Tian Xing—

09:52.560 --> 09:53.530
he

09:53.530 --> 09:55.320
has also shown us

09:56.080 --> 09:59.800
that the national selection exam is
indeed beneficial to Nine Cities

09:59.800 --> 10:03.050
in selecting more and better talents.

10:04.680 --> 10:06.170
These youngsters

10:06.170 --> 10:09.130
have our style when we were young.

10:09.130 --> 10:10.010
Not bad!

10:10.010 --> 10:11.760
They're really not bad, Zheng!

10:13.900 --> 10:15.660
We three old guys

10:15.740 --> 10:18.290
should start planning for the future.

10:19.200 --> 10:20.060
How about this?

10:20.800 --> 10:22.930
After we're done drinking tonight,

10:23.320 --> 10:24.250
let's go

10:24.250 --> 10:25.580
see the world together!

10:26.950 --> 10:27.920
Well, actually,

10:27.940 --> 10:30.260
I'd rather go to the fields,

10:30.290 --> 10:32.580
farm, fish,

10:32.610 --> 10:35.160
and live a carefree and leisurely life.

10:35.790 --> 10:37.290
How wonderful that would be.

10:37.290 --> 10:38.800
What's the fun in that?

10:39.560 --> 10:41.400
Okay, good.

10:41.800 --> 10:43.180
It's up to you.

10:43.890 --> 10:45.480
Up to you.

10:47.210 --> 10:48.760
-Cheers.
-Cheers.

10:55.410 --> 10:56.930
There will eventually be

10:56.960 --> 10:58.410
an end.

10:59.250 --> 11:01.130
Let's drink to that.

11:05.680 --> 11:06.320
Drink up.

11:06.930 --> 11:07.770
Okay...

11:08.320 --> 11:09.290
Drink up.

11:11.600 --> 11:12.600
Continue.

11:30.140 --> 11:31.280
Lyu!

12:28.320 --> 12:30.320
Lord Fan, you may get out of here now.

12:31.840 --> 12:32.770
Now?

12:33.080 --> 12:34.170
We've got a message from the Residence,

12:34.170 --> 12:35.960
saying that the Governor is
not doing well.

12:35.960 --> 12:37.840
You are requested to go over immediately.

12:37.840 --> 12:39.570
What happened to the Governor?

13:28.890 --> 13:29.600
Lord Tian!

13:29.600 --> 13:30.840
Please come with me to the Qi Residence!

13:30.840 --> 13:32.910
The Governor is in critical condition!

13:32.910 --> 13:33.790
What?

13:36.400 --> 13:38.400
The Governor urgently summons you.

13:39.600 --> 13:41.600
The Governor urgently summons you!

13:42.290 --> 13:45.290
The Governor orders you
to go to the Residence at once.

14:00.790 --> 14:01.910
Dark Wolf Token.

14:05.290 --> 14:06.530
Dark Wolf?

14:07.010 --> 14:08.930
The Dark Wolf who once saved me?

14:09.050 --> 14:10.050
He's amazing.

14:11.360 --> 14:12.600
He's not

14:13.320 --> 14:14.580
usually that amazing.

14:15.200 --> 14:16.710
Anyway, just remember that

14:16.710 --> 14:18.510
there are multiple Dark Wolves.

14:18.890 --> 14:20.350
The Wolves of Wind he leads

14:20.650 --> 14:23.180
served
as the late governor's secret bureau.

14:23.650 --> 14:24.800
Once you show the token,

14:24.800 --> 14:25.560
they'll execute

14:25.560 --> 14:27.020
every order without fail.

14:27.170 --> 14:28.320
If something happens

14:28.320 --> 14:30.170
that neither of us can handle,

14:31.080 --> 14:32.540
just take it to find Hu Die.

14:32.960 --> 14:34.760
And she'll find the Dark Wolves.

14:52.080 --> 14:53.130
What happened to the Governor?

14:53.130 --> 14:54.370
I really have no idea.

14:55.440 --> 14:57.240
Did something critical happen?

14:57.320 --> 14:59.650
I was also called over here
all of a sudden.

15:00.570 --> 15:02.250
I'm wondering how the Governor is doing.

15:02.250 --> 15:03.010
Lord Tian,

15:03.370 --> 15:05.370
didn't they say earlier today
that he was getting better

15:05.370 --> 15:06.700
and only needed to rest?

15:07.220 --> 15:09.720
How come he suddenly
took a turn for the worse?

15:09.720 --> 15:11.780
I was also called over here suddenly.

15:11.930 --> 15:13.730
I haven't seen the Governor yet.

15:30.850 --> 15:32.500
[Hall of Political Affairs]

15:33.680 --> 15:34.440
Lord Fan,

15:34.840 --> 15:35.840
this way, please.

15:36.770 --> 15:37.560
Tian Xing?

15:37.890 --> 15:38.480
Fan Yun?

15:40.050 --> 15:40.720
Why

15:41.400 --> 15:42.440
are you all here?

15:48.800 --> 15:50.460
Why are you locking us up here?

15:51.440 --> 15:52.720
Who exactly are you?

15:53.480 --> 15:54.410
Where is the Governor?

15:54.410 --> 15:55.870
How is the Governor doing?

16:01.130 --> 16:02.200
Why did he close the door?

16:02.200 --> 16:03.680
-Yeah, why?
-I don't know.

16:03.680 --> 16:05.080
What's going on here?

16:08.120 --> 16:08.920
Oh, no.

16:10.650 --> 16:11.710
We fell into a trap!

16:12.410 --> 16:13.530
-A trap?
-This is a trap?

16:13.530 --> 16:14.440
What? How...

16:23.300 --> 16:24.760
-Lord Zheng.
-Lord Zheng.

16:25.720 --> 16:26.720
By orders from above,

16:26.720 --> 16:28.200
the Governor is ill and needs rest;

16:28.200 --> 16:30.000
no one is allowed to disturb him.

16:31.990 --> 16:34.390
Do you even dare to stop me?

16:34.890 --> 16:35.930
This is my duty.

16:35.930 --> 16:37.860
Please don't blame me, Lord Zheng.

16:44.320 --> 16:46.050
I have the Supervisor's Token.

16:47.010 --> 16:49.340
I am here to send medicine
to the Governor.

16:49.960 --> 16:50.690
Understood!

17:12.329 --> 17:13.329
Your Excellency.

17:14.760 --> 17:15.890
Your Excellency?

17:25.890 --> 17:28.620
I entered the Residence
in the middle of the night

17:28.760 --> 17:30.730
and disturbed your sleep.

17:31.130 --> 17:33.190
Please forgive me, Your Excellency.

17:35.170 --> 17:37.030
Elder Zheng, what brings you here

17:37.440 --> 17:38.410
so late at night?

17:40.510 --> 17:42.370
There is an urgent document

17:43.330 --> 17:45.190
for you to sign, Your Excellency.

18:14.680 --> 18:16.480
Elder Zheng, you want me to admit

18:16.520 --> 18:18.850
the failure
of the national selection exam,

18:18.850 --> 18:20.530
abolish it,

18:22.890 --> 18:26.020
and even swear in the name
of the Governor of Nine Cities,

18:26.040 --> 18:27.700
without going back on my word?

18:28.370 --> 18:29.330
Exactly.

18:30.330 --> 18:31.340
After you sign it,

18:31.480 --> 18:34.390
I will announce it
to the public immediately.

18:34.930 --> 18:35.810
By then,

18:36.410 --> 18:37.410
the nobles

18:38.000 --> 18:40.610
will definitely feel grateful to you,
Your Excellency.

18:40.610 --> 18:41.210
However,

18:41.700 --> 18:44.500
if you go back on your word again,
Your Excellency,

18:44.570 --> 18:45.900
the Nine Noble Families

18:46.850 --> 18:48.510
will absolutely not tolerate

18:48.720 --> 18:50.850
their dignity being trampled upon again.

18:50.850 --> 18:52.680
And even the common people

18:52.680 --> 18:53.790
will never

18:56.200 --> 18:58.400
believe you anymore, Your Excellency.

18:59.370 --> 19:02.430
Elder Zheng,
you are really efficient and thoughtful.

19:03.720 --> 19:07.170
You've even drafted
this letter of self-condemnation for me.

19:07.170 --> 19:09.030
Please sign it, Your Excellency.

19:25.680 --> 19:26.890
Lord Zhang.

19:27.680 --> 19:28.680
Attendant Wei?

19:29.240 --> 19:31.700
The Governor has ordered us
to open the gate.

19:31.850 --> 19:33.110
What's going on today?

19:33.440 --> 19:35.330
So many lords just entered the Residence.

19:35.330 --> 19:36.810
They were all in a hurry.

19:38.520 --> 19:39.520
Nothing.

19:39.850 --> 19:41.510
You just need to open the gate.

19:46.610 --> 19:48.270
This is the Governor's token.

19:48.520 --> 19:49.930
Can you bear the consequences

19:49.930 --> 19:51.860
of delaying any important matter?

19:52.680 --> 19:53.480
Open the gate!

20:40.850 --> 20:42.510
I will pick it up every time

20:42.960 --> 20:44.960
you throw it away, Your Excellency.

20:45.280 --> 20:46.310
I will wait

20:46.520 --> 20:48.200
until you calm down

20:48.760 --> 20:49.970
and sign it.

20:53.520 --> 20:55.380
Please sign it, Your Excellency.

20:55.650 --> 20:56.440
Guards!

20:57.170 --> 20:58.720
Escort Lord Zheng out!

20:59.850 --> 21:02.240
Please sign it, Your Excellency.

21:23.170 --> 21:23.970
Zheng Yuan,

21:25.520 --> 21:27.780
do you know what you're doing is treason?

21:30.760 --> 21:32.570
Please forgive me, Your Excellency.

21:32.570 --> 21:34.410
I have no other choice.

21:35.890 --> 21:39.100
Once you sign
the letter of self-condemnation,

21:39.520 --> 21:42.380
I am willing to bear all the consequences.

21:44.040 --> 21:45.810
What if I insist on not signing?

21:46.850 --> 21:49.280
Are you going to kill me today?

21:53.810 --> 21:56.130
Your Excellency,
you are the only one left carrying

21:56.130 --> 21:58.460
the Qi family's bloodline in Nine Cities.

21:59.610 --> 22:02.240
I have no intention of treason,

22:02.810 --> 22:04.610
but today, Your Excellency, you

22:04.720 --> 22:06.180
have lost your direction.

22:06.760 --> 22:07.610
By order

22:07.930 --> 22:10.280
of the late governor, I am responsible

22:10.280 --> 22:12.240
for assisting you in political affairs.

22:12.240 --> 22:13.890
I can no longer just stand by

22:13.890 --> 22:16.280
and see you, Your Excellency,
be deceived by sycophants

22:16.280 --> 22:17.680
without doing anything.

22:18.090 --> 22:19.240
When necessary,

22:19.240 --> 22:20.060
I must

22:20.330 --> 22:22.260
eliminate the root of the problem.

22:28.200 --> 22:29.000
I once thought

22:29.000 --> 22:31.200
you would observe Fan Yun and the others

22:31.200 --> 22:33.330
and eventually change your attitude.

22:34.130 --> 22:36.190
Why are you so stubborn, Elder Zheng?

22:36.890 --> 22:39.890
You are too involved
to see clearly, Your Excellency!

22:45.090 --> 22:47.480
I watched you grow up,

22:48.650 --> 22:50.270
so I can see things clearly.

22:51.410 --> 22:53.240
Were it not for the slander of Fan Yun,

22:53.240 --> 22:54.440
Tian Xing,

22:55.570 --> 22:57.430
and others,

22:57.810 --> 22:58.680
you would

22:58.680 --> 23:01.080
certainly not be so blindly obstinate now!

23:12.910 --> 23:14.000
I see.

23:15.680 --> 23:17.370
What did you do...

23:18.090 --> 23:20.240
What did you do to Fan Yun and the others?

23:20.240 --> 23:22.240
Do you want me
to suffer agony worse than death?

23:22.240 --> 23:24.400
You are so wrong, Your Excellency.

23:27.370 --> 23:28.760
What I seek is

23:28.760 --> 23:31.480
a long-term grand plan for Nine Cities.

23:32.040 --> 23:33.900
I'm just asking you one question.

23:35.170 --> 23:36.960
Where is Fan Yun right now?

23:39.280 --> 23:40.170
Right now,

23:40.810 --> 23:42.170
Fan Yun also has

23:42.810 --> 23:44.140
a letter of resignation

23:44.200 --> 23:45.760
in front of her.

23:47.200 --> 23:49.520
Even if you don't sign this,

23:49.520 --> 23:52.090
once Fan Yun
and the other selection exam officials

23:52.090 --> 23:54.170
sign the letters of resignation,

23:54.890 --> 23:56.490
the national selection exam

23:56.960 --> 23:57.960
will eventually

23:58.410 --> 24:00.650
fizzle out.

24:15.930 --> 24:17.070
Sign it.

24:28.470 --> 24:29.930
None of them can be opened.

24:30.050 --> 24:30.890
How is it?

24:39.130 --> 24:40.930
It won't open. Still won't open.

24:42.370 --> 24:43.300
We can't get out.

24:43.480 --> 24:44.090
Fan Yun,

24:44.810 --> 24:46.540
it seems we're trapped inside.

24:49.410 --> 24:50.340
Tian Xing, look.

24:50.940 --> 24:52.470
The people trapped here are

24:53.090 --> 24:55.890
all civilian officials
from this selection exam.

24:56.500 --> 24:57.980
-Yeah.
-Indeed.

24:58.000 --> 25:00.330
Who told you
the Governor is critically ill,

25:00.330 --> 25:01.930
and who told you to come here?

25:02.440 --> 25:04.440
He... He was in our official uniform,

25:04.440 --> 25:06.410
holding a document
with the Supervisor's seal,

25:06.410 --> 25:07.170
so we all

25:07.200 --> 25:08.260
followed him here.

25:08.650 --> 25:10.000
Yes, that's exactly what happened.

25:10.000 --> 25:11.170
Yeah, me, too.

25:11.170 --> 25:12.470
This is indeed fishy.

25:13.380 --> 25:14.850
If this person got the news

25:15.130 --> 25:16.990
in the middle of the night like us,

25:17.330 --> 25:18.480
why would he

25:18.930 --> 25:21.860
specifically wear an official uniform
to inform us?

25:22.410 --> 25:23.760
Seeing him in an official uniform

25:23.760 --> 25:25.200
with the Supervisor's seal,

25:25.200 --> 25:26.330
and hearing the news

25:26.330 --> 25:28.280
of the Governor's critical condition,

25:28.280 --> 25:29.960
any official would follow along,

25:29.960 --> 25:31.000
I believe.

25:41.240 --> 25:42.280
Lady Fan Yun.

25:43.520 --> 25:44.240
Zheng Yi?

25:45.410 --> 25:47.340
Why are you in an official uniform?

25:50.300 --> 25:51.360
Here we meet again.

25:52.720 --> 25:53.280
Was it

25:53.810 --> 25:54.720
you who did it?

25:55.720 --> 25:57.570
You tricked us into coming here?

25:58.700 --> 25:59.510
Tricked?

25:59.570 --> 26:00.700
I wouldn't say that.

26:01.240 --> 26:02.000
However,

26:02.480 --> 26:03.850
it was indeed my doing.

26:10.570 --> 26:11.810
Where is the Governor?

26:11.810 --> 26:13.330
How is His Excellency doing?

26:13.330 --> 26:14.330
His Excellency is

26:14.610 --> 26:16.930
currently safe and sound.

26:18.000 --> 26:18.810
"Currently"?

26:20.170 --> 26:21.100
What do you mean?

26:21.810 --> 26:22.610
Could it be...

26:23.200 --> 26:24.090
Could it be that

26:24.520 --> 26:26.780
you're planning to hurt His Excellency?

26:27.570 --> 26:28.440
Lady Fan,

26:29.030 --> 26:30.640
I would never dare to bear

26:30.960 --> 26:32.650
such a heinous charge.

26:33.440 --> 26:34.730
However, Lord Fan,

26:34.850 --> 26:36.530
it's not hard to see His Excellency

26:36.530 --> 26:37.440
if you want to.

26:38.280 --> 26:39.270
Before you do,

26:39.440 --> 26:41.040
there is a small matter

26:41.610 --> 26:43.290
for you, Lady Fan Yun

26:43.570 --> 26:44.830
and everyone else,

26:45.130 --> 26:46.330
to handle.

26:47.370 --> 26:49.170
-What matter?
-What is it?

26:49.760 --> 26:52.280
I don't know. Do you?

26:55.930 --> 26:57.240
This is...

27:01.650 --> 27:02.720
Letter of resignation?

27:02.720 --> 27:03.760
I see.

27:05.090 --> 27:06.270
So you want us

27:06.520 --> 27:08.170
to voluntarily give up our positions

27:08.170 --> 27:10.500
and never serve as an official ever again.

27:11.410 --> 27:12.570
In your dreams.

27:13.570 --> 27:15.930
Bring ink and brushes for the lords.

27:15.930 --> 27:16.480
Yes.

27:20.130 --> 27:20.930
Don't bother.

27:23.280 --> 27:24.680
Just give up on this idea.

27:25.240 --> 27:26.330
We won't sign it.

27:43.980 --> 27:45.140
Lady Fan Yun,

27:46.090 --> 27:48.200
I don't want to make things
difficult for you.

27:48.200 --> 27:49.440
But as you also know,

27:50.280 --> 27:51.960
we both serve our respective masters,

27:51.960 --> 27:53.760
each performing our own duties.

27:54.240 --> 27:56.180
How about we talk nicely

27:56.810 --> 27:58.010
and save some dignity

27:58.410 --> 27:59.650
for each other?

28:01.440 --> 28:03.300
"Serve our respective masters"?

28:03.910 --> 28:05.170
You're blindly loyal,

28:05.480 --> 28:06.930
and you guys are rebelling, you know?

28:06.930 --> 28:08.170
Lady Fan Yun!

28:09.130 --> 28:10.850
We don't need your lecture!

28:12.080 --> 28:13.150
I, Zheng Yi,

28:13.200 --> 28:14.850
have lived most of my life.

28:14.850 --> 28:15.960
I had followed my master

28:15.960 --> 28:17.420
even before you were born.

28:18.290 --> 28:19.760
I've been through wars,

28:19.930 --> 28:21.370
famines,

28:21.370 --> 28:22.890
and prosperous times!

28:23.680 --> 28:25.560
I witnessed Nine Cities

28:26.090 --> 28:28.170
getting better little by little!

28:30.370 --> 28:32.360
My master has worked hard

28:32.890 --> 28:34.620
for Nine Cities his whole life.

28:35.440 --> 28:37.240
He is the most loyal subject

28:37.240 --> 28:38.960
of Nine Cities!

28:41.760 --> 28:43.130
But you guys

28:43.850 --> 28:45.480
want to burn bridges

28:46.130 --> 28:48.330
and ruin my master's reputation!

28:50.890 --> 28:53.040
You are truly ambitious

28:53.410 --> 28:54.960
and deserve to die!

28:55.470 --> 28:56.070
You...

28:58.170 --> 28:59.070
But Zheng Yi,

28:59.440 --> 29:00.810
has it ever occurred to you

29:00.810 --> 29:02.410
that what Lord Zheng is doing right now

29:02.410 --> 29:04.040
is exactly going to ruin Nine Cities
and the cause

29:04.040 --> 29:05.770
he's fought for his whole life?

29:05.930 --> 29:06.890
My master said,

29:07.830 --> 29:09.180
"Let history judge

29:09.810 --> 29:11.410
whether I'm right or wrong."

29:12.680 --> 29:13.650
Lady Fan Yun,

29:14.090 --> 29:15.330
you have to sign

29:16.000 --> 29:17.200
this document today,

29:17.720 --> 29:18.520
whether you

29:19.170 --> 29:20.170
like it or not.

29:28.720 --> 29:29.980
You can't threaten me.

29:30.810 --> 29:31.960
I get what I want,

29:32.930 --> 29:34.660
and I'll die for a worthy cause.

29:34.760 --> 29:35.720
I won't sign it.

29:36.200 --> 29:39.000
-We won't sign it either.
-We won't sign it either.

29:41.200 --> 29:42.160
Right now,

29:42.440 --> 29:45.170
there is also a document
in front of the Governor.

29:45.330 --> 29:46.890
Once His Excellency signs it,

29:46.890 --> 29:49.950
the national selection exam
will be a thing of the past.

29:50.440 --> 29:51.970
What you are holding onto is

29:52.130 --> 29:53.590
nothing but a joke.

29:56.130 --> 29:57.280
Lady Fan Yun,

29:58.130 --> 29:59.370
I'm not here

30:00.200 --> 30:02.170
to kill you guys today.

30:03.240 --> 30:05.280
Don't make pointless sacrifices.

30:24.480 --> 30:25.410
Zheng?

30:26.440 --> 30:27.240
Zheng.

30:38.280 --> 30:39.330
Zhao.

30:40.370 --> 30:41.480
Sober up.

30:42.890 --> 30:43.630
Wake up!

30:47.040 --> 30:48.660
No, Zheng...

30:51.770 --> 30:54.770
Zheng must have given us fake alcohol.

30:56.520 --> 30:57.660
My head is

30:58.000 --> 31:00.720
throbbing right now.

31:01.850 --> 31:05.280
Come on, stop throbbing.

31:05.280 --> 31:07.960
Zheng is gone.
There are only the two of us here.

31:07.960 --> 31:09.280
And you're still throbbing.

31:09.280 --> 31:11.040
Hey...

31:16.200 --> 31:17.730
Where is your access badge?

31:23.830 --> 31:24.590
Oh, no.

31:25.570 --> 31:26.500
What do you mean?

31:27.720 --> 31:29.580
He's going to do something crazy.

31:53.040 --> 31:55.240
Lord Zhao, please don't go any further!

32:01.890 --> 32:03.130
What are you doing?

32:04.680 --> 32:06.630
How dare you block my way?

32:07.200 --> 32:08.160
Back then,

32:08.370 --> 32:11.400
I could kill a general
among a large, strong army!

32:12.200 --> 32:14.040
Do you think just the few of you

32:14.440 --> 32:16.100
can stop us today?

32:16.760 --> 32:17.610
Normally,

32:17.610 --> 32:18.960
we're definitely no match for you.

32:18.960 --> 32:20.420
But it is different today.

32:21.200 --> 32:21.810
Zhao,

32:22.440 --> 32:23.300
how do you feel?

32:23.680 --> 32:24.440
I'm fine!

32:42.850 --> 32:43.520
You...

32:47.040 --> 32:47.700
Fine.

32:49.130 --> 32:50.330
If you want to kill me,

32:51.000 --> 32:52.090
go ahead!

32:53.280 --> 32:54.330
Lady Fan Yun,

32:54.730 --> 32:55.700
I'm sorry.

33:26.810 --> 33:27.480
Zheng Yi,

33:28.240 --> 33:30.240
you have nothing left to fight with.

33:30.280 --> 33:31.140
Surrender now!

33:33.850 --> 33:34.520
Dad,

33:34.920 --> 33:36.260
why is it you?

33:36.410 --> 33:37.200
Am I cool?

33:37.480 --> 33:38.000
Fan Yun.

33:39.340 --> 33:39.820
Gao Ran?

33:40.480 --> 33:40.960
Dad...

33:40.980 --> 33:42.810
It's dangerous here! Get out of here!

33:42.810 --> 33:43.340
Let's go.

33:43.570 --> 33:44.240
Let's go!

33:44.810 --> 33:46.240
-Let's go.
-Let's go

34:02.610 --> 34:03.680
-Run!
-Hurry!

34:06.370 --> 34:07.190
Elders, please go quickly.

34:07.190 --> 34:08.350
Zhao, hurry!

34:09.030 --> 34:11.159
We must ensure the Governor's safety!

34:15.389 --> 34:16.550
What are you doing?

34:16.960 --> 34:17.810
Zheng!

34:23.000 --> 34:23.920
Zheng...
